the preceding interview, which when|ever
<PB N="102" REF="104">
he approached her &s;eemed to trem|ble
on his lips.</P>
<P>Night returned, and Ferdinand re|paired
to the chamber of Julia to pur|&s;ue
his enquiry. Here he had not long
